Reviews

People say that live songs are always better than album versions and this 

album really proves that. Great acts like Alanis Morrisette, Eric Clapton and
Bryan Adams all feature in this outstanding album. A smooth CD to chill
out to in the evenings or on a hot summers afternoon. The very best 
performances come from Seal with Kiss From A Rose, which sounds 

incredible and is so moving. Secoindly theres Noel Gallagher singing
Don&#039;t Look Back in Anger, Liam sings this on Whats the Story but Noel
has the better voice and this track really shows it off. Buy this album now and chill.
